chipmunk.unlimited.feedback

Class TimeEditParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • AsyncHttpResponseHandler
      • chipmunk.unlimited.feedback.TimeEditParser

  • public class TimeEditParser
extends AsyncHttpResponseHandler
    The TimeEdit HTML is full of errors, causing the w3c.dom-parser to fail. As a result, scavenging the HTML for data is the only solution to integrate TimeEdit communication. This class is forked from TobbenTM's implementation of a TimeEdit parser. Most of the code is poorly documented and hard to follow, and should in case of severe modification needs be replaced entirely. The source of the fork: https://github.com/TobbenTM/HiG-TimeEdit-Reader/blob/645e939dee31c249c135ea5b216890fcd92f8537/java/com/tobbentm/higreader/TimeParser.java
